resources.string:
"When Autonavi NLP (Network Location Provider) function is opened, you will allow AutoNavi NLP service to collect anonymous location data. Some data may be encrypted and stored on your device. Encryption and collection may occur even when no apps are running. You may be charged for data traffic. The collected anonymous location data will be used for improving the performance and accuracy of the location service. Autonavi promises the collected anonymous location data will not be provided to others or be used for other purposes except to render services. The data to be collected includes the followings:
- ID, Signal Strength of WLAN AP to be surveyed from the periphery;
- ID, Signal Strength to be surveyed from the peripheral base station (for GSM);
- ID, Signal Strength to be surveyed from the peripheral base station (for CDMA)."
